name: one of a kind hand made clothing
description:
My name is Genessa
I manufacture and  create one of a kind pieces. All of my work is made to last.

 The thing I love about one of a kind is that no one else will ever be wearing what you purchase. I personally  think clothing is a big part of who you are, it's like art, it defines you.

I make women's wear, men's wear, children clothing,  bedding and curtains.
